[10.526721, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[35B\u001b[38;2;177;185;249m/review-fix-ship                                            (total-recall) Use when asked to \"review and improve\", \"review ; fix ; commit\", \"harden and ship\", or any iterative\r\u001b[62C\u001b[1Breview-fix-ship loop on a git repository. Drives a closed loop until git status is clean — read the code, propose fixes with …\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m/init                                                       Initialize a new CLAUDE.md file with codebase documentation\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B/memory-workflow                                            (total-recall) Use when storing or retrieving memories with the Total Recall plugin — establishes the cheapest-first retrieval\r\u001b[62C\u001b[1Border (injected index → get_memories_by_keys → search_index → recall_memory), the knowledge-capture rules (executive summary,…\u001b[39m\u001b[45;1H\u001b[42;4H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
